			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2115297">
									

<p>Two problems essentially&#8230; I have a back story in mind for Cimmerian(and yeah he's a character in my headcanon), and I want the page to be somewhat serious. Until I actually get around to writing about him (and I won't feel comfortable enough with that until I've written quite at least a tale or two), I don't wanna restrict where I can take that story.</p>
<p>On the other hand, I've been working towards being able to make this page since I wrote my first skip a little over a month ago. So it's up and it's bare bones for now. ;)</p>
<p>Though&#8230; I don't know that I'll be adding much beyond a bio and a physical description.</p>

